document_data.name: Estrip Rosznar
document_data.mainbody: '''Estrip Rosznar''', who was nicknamed the '''Young Masked Lady''', was a [[noble]] inhabiting [[Waterdeep]], City of Splendors, during the mid-to-late 14{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Description: She resembled [[Lhestyn]]â€”an [[Open Lord]] of Waterdeep who was called "the Masked Lady." Estrip enjoyed wearing masks as part of her costume for dances.
document_data.Activities:
Estrip was part of the [[Rosznar]] [[Nobility of Waterdeep|noble family]] of Waterdeep. She lived within [[Rosznar Villa]] on [[Thunderstaff Way]] in Waterdeep's [[Waterdeep/Sea Ward|Sea Ward]].

She died around the {{YearlinkName|1372}}.{{Cite web enhancement/Noble Houses of Waterdeep|8}}
